import React from 'react';
import { FaHtml5,FaCss3Alt,FaBootstrap } from 'react-icons/fa';
import { IconContext } from 'react-icons/lib';
import {
  PricingSection,
  PricingWrapper,
  PricingHeading,
  PricingContainer,
  PricingCard,
  PricingCardInfo,
  PricingCardIcon,
  PricingCardPlan,
  PricingCardCost
} from './Skils.elements';

function Skils() {
  return (
    <IconContext.Provider value={{ color: '#a9b3c1', size: 64 }}>
      <PricingSection>
        <PricingWrapper>
          <PricingHeading>Skills</PricingHeading>
          <PricingContainer>

            <PricingCard to='/sign-up'>
              <PricingCardInfo>
                <PricingCardIcon>
                  <FaHtml5 />
                </PricingCardIcon>
                <PricingCardPlan>HTML 5</PricingCardPlan>
                <PricingCardCost>$99.99</PricingCardCost>
                
                
                
              </PricingCardInfo>
            </PricingCard>
            
            <PricingCard to='/sign-up'>
              <PricingCardInfo>
                <PricingCardIcon>
                  <FaCss3Alt />
                </PricingCardIcon>
                <PricingCardPlan>CSS 3</PricingCardPlan>
                <PricingCardCost>$299.99</PricingCardCost>
                
                
                
              </PricingCardInfo>
            </PricingCard>

            <PricingCard to='/sign-up'>
              <PricingCardInfo>
                <PricingCardIcon>
                  <FaBootstrap />
                </PricingCardIcon>
                <PricingCardPlan>Diamond Kings</PricingCardPlan>
                <PricingCardCost>$999.99</PricingCardCost>
                
                
                
              </PricingCardInfo>
            </PricingCard>
            <PricingCard to='/sign-up'>
              <PricingCardInfo>
                <PricingCardIcon>
                  <FaHtml5 />
                </PricingCardIcon>
                <PricingCardPlan>Diamond Kings</PricingCardPlan>
                <PricingCardCost>$999.99</PricingCardCost>
                
               
                
              </PricingCardInfo>
            </PricingCard>

          </PricingContainer>
        </PricingWrapper>
      </PricingSection>
    </IconContext.Provider>
  );
}
export default Skils;
